Class Registration

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ncl.jcarlton.objects.Registration

  • public final class Registration
extends java.lang.Object

    Registration

    The representation of a car registration. This class enforces uniqueness, to ensure that no two registrations can be the same.
    Author:
    Jonathan Carlton
